Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}胸の痛みも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}つたう涙も
