Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.20,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}生きよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不器用な愛が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.90,ED_JP,,0,0,10,,{\fad(240,240)}花を咲かすまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:43.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.19,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}就算有一天
